30025000.text:
Why is the package taking so long to get here?
I'd better contact the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>shipping company</>...

30025001.text: Now that the materials are here, let's start repairs.

30025002.text:
I'm really very busy.
Without me, the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Peach Blossom</> wouldn't even be able to operate.

30025003.text:
I just can't trust the work of everyone under me.
I have to double check everything.

30025004.text:
It's the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Oduksini</> again?
How are we supposed to work if we don't have charcoal?

30025005.text:
We should put out all urgent fires first...
No, wait! We should keep the fire, not put it out!

30025006.text: They said making a profit would be so easy here at <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Haewol</>...

30025007.text: The most <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Haewol</>-like thing to do is to be creative!

30025008.text:
Drat, I can't do it.
I can't work, not even if the older <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Sol Seekers</> came here.

30025009.text:
Come to think of it, I wasn't really acting mature, either...
I'll work on it and do better.

30025010.text: Clean water! Delicious food! Let's protect it, meow!

30025011.text: What do we do...? We're in big trouble.

30025012.text:
We need to be careful.
The <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Mudlands</> are too dangerous.

30025013.text: It's too dangerous. We should make it off limits to people...

30025014.text:
Don't you misunderstand us, hoo hoo!
We don't attack people, hoo hoo!

30025016.text: Hmm... How do we overcome this?

30025017.text: We don't have any materials... Can't we rest a bit?

30025018.text: There's still a lot of things to do at <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Dojung Port</>.

30025019.text: It's all good, but let's eat first.

30025021.text: Managing a facility is endless work.

30025022.text: Eating after finishing work is heaven.

30025023.text: Working, organizing documents, I'm so busy.

30025024.text: I should ask them to send me to somewhere other than <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Dojung Port</>.

30025025.text:
Don't open your mouth and just get to work.
Ah... I shouldn't have even said that...

30025026.text:
It feels good to think the gear I make
is used all over <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Haewol</>.

30025027.text: I've been tricked... I lost everything...

30025028.text:
I came here because of my faith in the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Saho</>...
You can’t do this to me!

30025029.text: I’m never doing business with the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Peach Blossom</> again.

30025030.text: We have to complain as a group.

30025031.text: I need to work hard... I have a family to feed!

30025032.text: The surroundings are so dangerous. How do you expect me to settle here?

30025033.text: They told me that I could trust them and that <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Haewol</> is safe!

30025034.text: I didn't come here to be treated like this...

30025035.text: It's probably because we don't have any power...

30025036.text: It's all in the name of success.

30025037.text: Ah, who can help me deal with my frustrations?

30025039.text: I feel tired today. When does my shift end?

30025040.text: Will <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Ko Gondae</> be on patrol today, too?

30025041.text:
My uniform is too heavy.
I wish they made it lighter...

30025042.text:
We need a lot of <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>moss</>...
Would it be better to grow it, meow?

30025043.text: There's lots of good herbs here, meow!

30025044.text: Don't worry too much, they'll come back safely.

30025045.text: I bet they'll return tomorrow, so it should be no big deal.

30025046.text: It's too dangerous. We should make it off limits to people...
